data.description:
Giuseppe and the Lion is a premier Italian and Sushi restaurant located in Naples, Florida with live entertainment. We have quickly become a beloved culinary destination for locals and visitors alike bringing cutting edge dining and music together in perfect harmony.  Our founders, Joseph Sutherland (Giuseppe) and Leo Hertzog (The Lion) have always had a passion for creating exceptional dining experiences, and this is evident in every aspect of our restaurant.

At Giuseppe and the Lion, we believe that great food should be paired with exceptional service. Our team is dedicated to providing every guest with an unforgettable dining experience, from the moment they walk through our doors. Whether you're looking for a romantic dinner for two or a lively gathering with friends and family. We have the perfect table for you with inside and outside dining available. We have the perfect atmosphere to suit your needs.

With a team of talented employees, we strive to deliver the best Italian and Sushi cuisine on the Southwest Florida Coast. Our menu is carefully curated to showcase the freshest ingredients and flavors that will tantalize your taste buds. The dining experience is enhanced with our extensive wine list with each bottle stored to the proper temperature in our wine cuvee storage system (755 Bottle Capacity) coupled with our amazing bartenders serving all the tasty cocktails of your choice.

Thank you for considering Giuseppe and the Lion for your next dining experience. We look forward to serving you soon.
